article_id:73,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding the Kindness and Captivity Event [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue in the event Kindness and Captivity, taking place since <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540965600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Details of the issue</div><div>・Tapping the Trick or Treasure event banner on the Home Screen when Melsa&#39;s friendship has not been maxed causes a prompt to incorrectly appear, asking to remove her from your team.</div><div><br></div><div>■Fixed Issues: Updated <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1541493000"></span></div><div>・Some wind mana founts summoned by Hypnos in Hypnos Showdown: Standard do not take damage the first three seconds after they appear.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1540979100,update_time1542364179